---
title: Creamy Chicken Tikka-Style Bowls with Basmati and Toasted Flatbread
description: Creamy tikka sauce loaded with chicken, peas, peppers and onions is served with buttery basmati and warm garlic flatbread in this Indian-inspired dish.
